name: Rabbits Room
description:
Jump and climb around a procedural generated room.

Enter something(for example: cats) and click play, it will generate a room made of cubes evolved to look similar to what you enter. The generations/percent accuracy will be displayed, click play when you want to play!

Collect all the yellow orbs to 100% complete the level.

Check it out on the LDJam site http://ludumdare.com/compo/ludum-dare-37/?action=preview&uid=57236
